  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Available on Self-Catering basis. All rooms have a kitchenette or full kitchen. If you don't feel like cooking, the hotel also has two on site restaurants.</p>
<p><strong>Hy's Steakhouse</strong> is open for lunch and dinner and offers prime cuts of beef. There is also a sophisticated cocktail and wine bar. </p>
<p><strong>The Brickworks Public House</strong> has over largest selection of craft gins in Whistler. If you can't decide, choose a tasting flight with five different gins to try. The restaurant is also popular for its craft beers and signature dishes.</p>
<p><strong>Coffee Bike - </strong>located in the hotel lobby is the brand new coffee bike. Available every morning serving up barista coffee and some yummy breakfast items including breakfast wraps, vegan burritos, baked croissants, waffles and other goodies. </p>
<p><strong>Caramba Restaurant</strong> is located directly across from the hotel and served breakfast until noon. The restaurant serves up all the classics including eggs benedict, juices, coffee and the famous 'hangover sandwich' for anyone who experienced Whistler's popular night life.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
