  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Delta Whistler Village Suites is conveniently located in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> Village. You will be a ten minute walk away from the main lifts and you have plenty of shops, restaurants and cafes right on your doorstep.</p>
<h2>New Design</h2>
<p>The recently refurbished hotel has a modern feel using natural materials. The lobby and public areas are well furnished and a great place to chill out before hitting the slopes.</p>
<p>The new guestroom design is inspired by the Canadian landscape, with fresh modern colour palettes and a strong focus on maximising on natural light. Rooms have a multi-purpose area providing a docking system for mobiles and laptops and high speed internet access in all newly renovated rooms.</p>
<h2>Rooms &amp; Relaxation</h2>
<p>All rooms either have a kitchenette or full kitchen so it is easy to self-cater and some will have laundry facilities. With one and two bedroom suites sleeping up to six people, there is a room to suit everybody. Most rooms will have a fireplace and balcony to enjoy views over Whistler. </p>]]></description>
