  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Guest rooms </strong>sleep up to two people in a Queen bed. Rooms have a small kitchenette with microwave and fridge. Cots cannot be used in these rooms.</p>
<p><strong>One-Bedroom Suites </strong>sleep up to four people. The master bedroom will have Twin beds or a King or Queen size bed. There is a double sofa bed in the living area, gas fireplace, balcony, full kitchen with dishwasher, microwave and washer/dryer.</p>
<p><strong>Two-Bedroom Suites </strong>have a master bedroom will have a King or Queen size bed, a second bedroom with twin or queen size bed. The living area has a double sofa bed, gas fireplace, balcony, full kitchen with dishwasher, microwave and washer/dryer. They can sleep up to six people.</p>
<p>Please request bed type at time of booking, requests cannot be guaranteed. In order to guarantee bed configuration there may be a charge.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Full bathroom with bath or shower</li>
<li>Connectivity dock for laptop/ mobile phone</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
